1. The total amount of the Community financial contribution referred to in Article 1 shall be EUR 201172.
2. The maximum amount of the Community financial contribution for each concerned Member State shall be as follows:
(a) EUR 26904: Germany;
(b) EUR 45007: France;
(c) EUR 93030: Italy;
(d) EUR 36231: Sweden.
3. The maximum Community financial contribution for each inspection posts' strengthening programme shall be as set out in the Annex.
